<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 11:51:47 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a454fe62ff</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一些快速昆虫素描，灵感来源于莎拉·辛布莱特的《艺术家手绘本》，这是我从图书馆借来的几本艺术书之一。

用实体书做参考，而不是手机或电脑，感觉真好。把电子设备收起来，画画时身边只有纸张环绕，有种令人平静的东西。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An open sketchbook rests on a wooden table, displaying loose ink sketches of several insects. The page includes bees and wasps in flight near the top and a large stag beetle at the bottom, with light blue and green watercolor washes adding subtle background color." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a4a454fe62ff.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 11:51:47 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a3d0288ab3</link><description>&lt;p&gt;三口袋连帽卫衣&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Season 8" height="1622" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/selah/6a4a3d0288ab3.jpg" width="1320"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://selah.some.pics"&gt;@selah&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 11:16:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a3cd6ee4a3</link><description>&lt;p&gt;三口袋连帽卫衣&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Season 8" height="1629" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/selah/6a4a3cd6ee4a3.jpg" width="1320"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://selah.some.pics"&gt;@selah&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 11:15:37 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a3caf18151</link><description>&lt;p&gt;三口袋连帽卫衣&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Season 8" height="1622" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/selah/6a4a3caf18151.jpg" width="1320"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://selah.some.pics"&gt;@selah&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 11:14:57 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a1f72e3eeb</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我和老公与吉布森一家等人一起庆祝7月4日 🇺🇸&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A close-up outdoor selfie of a smiling woman with cat-eye glasses next to a man with dark-rimmed glasses giving a thumbs up. Both are wearing glow stick necklaces—hers is red and his is blue—against a background of green foliage." height="2785" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/6a4a1f72e3eeb.jpg" width="2087"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 09:10:17 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>